我尝试了Hololive的元宇宙“Holo Earth”上发布的沙盒游戏。这可能很有趣......！ https://www.moguravr.com/holo-earth-review-sand-box/ノンジャンル人生 Fri, 15 Dec 2023 10:22:43 +0000 VTuberホロライブサンドボックスホロアース https://www.moguravr.com/?p=242131 <p> Hololive Productions 的运营商 Cover Co., Ltd. 更新了元宇宙项目“Holo Earth”，并发布了多项限时功能。特别值得注意的是 Avatar Create 和 Sandbox。仍需验证[...]</p><p>这篇文章我<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/holo-earth-review-sand-box/">尝试了Hololive的元宇宙中发布的沙盒游戏“Holo Earth”这可能很有趣......！</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p> <a href="https://hololivepro.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Hololive Productions</a>运营公司<a href="https://cover-corp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cover Co., Ltd.</a>更新了元宇宙项目<strong>“</strong> <a href="https://holoearth.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Holo Earth</strong></a> <strong>”</strong> ，并发布了多项限时功能。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.fu3i065isez8-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.fu3i065isez8-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.fu3i065isez8-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.fu3i065isez8-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.fu3i065isez8-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>特别值得注意的是<strong>Avatar Create</strong>和<strong>Sandbox</strong> 。虽然目前还处于只准备了验证所需的最低限度功能的阶段，但看来未来可以期待更新。这次，我们将报道截至2023年12月14日0.5β更新的内容。</p><h2>创建你自己的头像</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.icill6bk9jkz-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.icill6bk9jkz-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.icill6bk9jkz-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.icill6bk9jkz-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.icill6bk9jkz-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.jku754ddlllt-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.jku754ddlllt-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.jku754ddlllt-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.jku754ddlllt-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.jku754ddlllt-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>在本次准备的头像创建功能中，您可以选择男性或女性类型并创建头像。两者都具有动漫风格的设计，即使与 Hololive 的 VTuber 放在一起也不会显得格格不入。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.k9jxspqqevib-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.k9jxspqqevib-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.k9jxspqqevib-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.k9jxspqqevib-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.k9jxspqqevib-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.bqqwd7bs5qht-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.bqqwd7bs5qht-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.bqqwd7bs5qht-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.bqqwd7bs5qht-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.bqqwd7bs5qht-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>在详细设置中，选择体型、脸部轮廓、眼睛、眉毛等部位。您可以更改头发的渐变和子颜色，但只有少数颜色和发型可用。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.kisa89tleaij-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.kisa89tleaij-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.kisa89tleaij-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.kisa89tleaij-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.kisa89tleaij-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>语音仅作为一项提供，似乎尚未实现。不过总体来说3D模型的质量还是很高的，感觉可以和市售游戏媲美。预计未来零件数量和颜色将会增加，因此您将能够创建更加独特的角色。</p><h2>具有作为沙盒的潜力</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.1xt7tcppjo1j-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.1xt7tcppjo1j-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.1xt7tcppjo1j-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.1xt7tcppjo1j-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.1xt7tcppjo1j-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>让我们立即用我们这次创建的头像来尝试一下沙盒吧！入口处有一位导航员角色<strong>“密特拉”</strong> ，他将为玩家指引方向。门口还有其他玩家的头像，看起来已经很忙碌了。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.h9v4j4nwx4tq-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.h9v4j4nwx4tq-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.h9v4j4nwx4tq-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.h9v4j4nwx4tq-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.h9v4j4nwx4tq-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>从入口处移动到模拟室。它的目的是模拟未探索地区的活动，似乎被定位为未来计划的全面沙箱的准备阶段。我的印象是空间一点也不大。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.hyzwfnq4osta-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.hyzwfnq4osta-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.hyzwfnq4osta-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.hyzwfnq4osta-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.hyzwfnq4osta-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.viw4nfolhvr3-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.viw4nfolhvr3-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.viw4nfolhvr3-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.viw4nfolhvr3-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.viw4nfolhvr3-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>不过，我觉得没什么可做的，而且内容让我很惊讶，比我想象的更有成就感。这是因为<strong>构成沙盒的基础</strong>已经牢固建立，<strong>材料采集、加工、建造等</strong>要素逐渐解锁，可做的事情越来越多。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.rakx8cs6fbvm-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.rakx8cs6fbvm-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.rakx8cs6fbvm-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.rakx8cs6fbvm-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.rakx8cs6fbvm-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>本教程首先创建一个所谓的“豆腐屋”，它只是一个被墙壁包围的底座。玩过《我的世界》的用户将能够毫不犹豫地玩这款游戏，因为游戏涉及从附近的树木、石头和觅食中收集材料。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.nxuafscufjpv-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.nxuafscufjpv-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.nxuafscufjpv-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.nxuafscufjpv-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.nxuafscufjpv-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.2nxf2z3mh9xu-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.2nxf2z3mh9xu-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.2nxf2z3mh9xu-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.2nxf2z3mh9xu-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.2nxf2z3mh9xu-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>真正的工作不是“只是建造一个临时住所而已”，而是从这里开始！我们将继续用正宗的工作台、烹饪台、熔炼炉等更新我们的工艺。原来是稻草房，后来演变成了木屋。你将能够制作家具并讲究室内设计（顺便说一句，还有制作和装饰衣服的元素，但到目前为止只有一种）。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.pnhbdvr2of9w-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.pnhbdvr2of9w-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.pnhbdvr2of9w-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.pnhbdvr2of9w-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.pnhbdvr2of9w-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>除了单独建造模拟房间外，您还可以将房间公开，并享受最多 20 人的沙盒。如果你想和朋友一起玩，还可以设置密码。</p><h2>年终和新年活动也在剧院室举行。</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.gg5qx7ujvfu7-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.gg5qx7ujvfu7-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.gg5qx7ujvfu7-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.gg5qx7ujvfu7-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.gg5qx7ujvfu7-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.v9t3gqw3s5bo-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.v9t3gqw3s5bo-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.v9t3gqw3s5bo-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.v9t3gqw3s5bo-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2023/12/8cab22db4b923b94e7e22f42041b39ab-kix.v9t3gqw3s5bo-768x432.webp 768w" width="1000" height="563" /></a></p><p>全息地球还设有向公众开放的<strong>“另类城市”</strong>区域和<strong>剧院区域</strong>。在这里，预计您将能够在年末元旦期间与其他用户一起享受Hololive直播活动和Hologura精选作品。此外，活动区域“新年京宫湖”将于年初限时向公众开放。</p><p>单击此处查看时间表。</p><blockquote><p>・12月29日（星期五）20:00-22:25“Hologura杰作精选第1部分”<br />・12月30日（周六）20:00-22:35“Hologura杰作精选第2部”<br />・12月31日（星期日）18:00-23:00“<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000001010.000030268.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yuku Holo Kuru Holo 2023▷2024~</a> ”<br />・1月1日（星期一）13:00-18:00“<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000999.000030268.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">绫文的“伊吕波二令人心寒的元旦”-可以蜷缩在被炉里的鬼物派对</a>”<br />・1月2日（星期二）20:00-22:25「Hologura杰作精选第1部」（重播）<br />・1月3日（周三）20:00-22:35「Hologura杰作精选第2部」（重播）</p></blockquote><p>在Cover Company，我们的愿景不仅包括Hololive Productions的管理，还包括未来元宇宙上用户之间的互动，而这次更新就是这一点的一瞥。 </p><div class="mg-mogura-card m-0 mb-2 mb-md-3"><div class="d-flex"><div class="mg-mogura-card-thumb position-relative"><img class="mg-img-cover position-absolute h-100 w-100" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2022/06/202206271133498000-300x169.jpg"></div><div class="card-body mg-card-text p-2 p-lg-3"><h3 class="h6 mt-0 mw-0 mb-1 p-0 card-title mg-card-title mg-text-break-all text-dark font-weight-normal"> Hololive的元宇宙“Holo Earth”的目标是什么？与业务人员一起体验正在开发的demo版本</h3><div class="text-gray mg-mogura-card-excerpt mb-1 my-md-2">Holo Earth是一款沙盒游戏，属于Cover Co., Ltd.目前正在开发的Metaverse项目的一部分。由异世界创作项目“Hololive Alternative”、“VTuber”和“Metaverse”诞生的项目......</div> <span class="badge badge-outline-live mg-mogura-card-badge px-2">Hololive</span> <span class="text-muted small ml-1">2022.06.27</span></div></div></div><p>请注意，Sandbox 已宣布，由于某些功能测试，游戏数据将定期重置，发布期后房间数据将被删除。全面运营开始后，内容可能会发生变化，敬请谅解。我们建议您先尝试一下该游戏，看看它是什么类型的游戏。</p><p><a href="https://holoearth.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>点击此处查看“Holo Earth”的分发目的地（兼容Windows PC，免费）</strong></a></p><p> （参考）<a href="https://holoearth.com/news/1115/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">新闻稿</a></p><p>这篇文章我<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/holo-earth-review-sand-box/">尝试了Hololive的元宇宙中发布的沙盒游戏“Holo Earth”这可能很有趣......！</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ;
